      "content": "hey so im a student in berlin and things are super stressful right now with finals coming up. im currently on sertraline for my mood but it feels like it's not quite doing enough to help with the anxiety/stress part. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine to help boost my mood naturally while i study. do u think it's okay to take them both together? i dont want to mess up my meds but i really need that extra lift right now.",
